 22/8 /18 Vecquemont A hot boil day . The 3rd Divis attack up front somewher and the 1st Divis go through them in the morn . The rumour is that we go in on the 25th . The Battalion parad at 9.30 a.m. under surround green tree and did Lewi gun and other work . Mill with his staff and a limber went all through the line and collar blanket and equip galor . Our new reinforc are settl down and should prove to be good men . They came via Panama Canal and U.S.A. Walk around and yarn to a lot of our old sergeant other . The ground down near the river here is peati and shake when a hors is ridden
